#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.laplace"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:1 of
msgid ""
"Draw samples from the Laplace or double exponential distribution with "
"specified location (or mean) and scale (decay)."
msgstr "从具有指定位置（或均值）和尺度（衰减）的拉普拉斯或双指数分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:4 of
msgid ""
"The Laplace distribution is similar to the Gaussian/normal distribution, "
"but is sharper at the peak and has fatter tails. It represents the "
"difference between two independent, identically distributed exponential "
"random variables."
msgstr ""
"拉普拉斯分布与高斯/正态分布相似，但在峰值处更尖锐，尾部更厚。它表示两个"
"独立且同分布的指数随机变量之间的差值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:9 of
msgid "The position, :math:`\\mu`, of the distribution peak. Default is 0."
msgstr "分布峰值的位置 :math:`\\mu`。默认为 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:11 of
msgid ":math:`\\lambda`, the exponential decay. Default is 1."
msgstr ":math:`\\lambda`，指数衰减。默认为 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:13 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``loc`` and ``scale`` are both scalars. Otherwise, "
"``np.broadcast(loc, scale).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定的形状是例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本"
"。如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），当 ``loc`` 和 ``scale`` 都是标量时返回"
"单个值。否则抽取 ``np.broadcast(loc, scale).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:18 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:20 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:22 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:25 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized Laplace distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的拉普拉斯分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:29 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:30 of
msgid "It has the probability density function"
msgstr "其概率密度函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:32 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"f(x; \\mu, \\lambda) = \\frac{1}{2\\lambda}\n"
"\\exp\\left(-\\frac{|x - \\mu|}{\\lambda}\\right).\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:35 of
msgid ""
"The first law of Laplace, from 1774, states that the frequency of an "
"error can be expressed as an exponential function of the absolute "
"magnitude of the error, which leads to the Laplace distribution. For many"
" problems in economics and health sciences, this distribution seems to "
"model the data better than the standard Gaussian distribution."
msgstr ""
"拉普拉斯第一定律（1774年）指出，误差的频率可以表示为误差绝对值的指数函数"
"，这导致了拉普拉斯分布。在经济学和健康科学的许多问题中，该分布似乎比标准"
"高斯分布更好地拟合数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:43 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:44 of
msgid ""
"Abramowitz, M. and Stegun, I. A. (Eds.). \"Handbook of Mathematical "
"Functions with Formulas, Graphs, and Mathematical Tables, 9th printing,\""
" New York: Dover, 1972."
msgstr ""
"Abramowitz, M. 和 Stegun, I. A.（编）。《数学函数手册：公式、图表和数学表"
"，第9版》，纽约：Dover，1972年。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:47 of
msgid ""
"Kotz, Samuel, et. al. \"The Laplace Distribution and Generalizations, \" "
"Birkhauser, 2001."
msgstr "Kotz, Samuel 等。《拉普拉斯分布及其推广》，Birkhauser，2001年。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:49 of
msgid ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. \"Laplace Distribution.\" From MathWorld--A Wolfram "
"Web Resource. http://mathworld.wolfram.com/LaplaceDistribution.html"
msgstr ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. “拉普拉斯分布。” 来自 MathWorld--Wolfram 网络资源。"
"http://mathworld.wolfram.com/LaplaceDistribution.html"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.laplace.laplace:52 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Laplace distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laplace_distribution"
msgstr ""
"Wikipedia，“拉普拉斯分布”，http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laplace_"
"distribution"

